# Input

```scss
@include button;

@include clearfix(
);

@include size(
$width,
$height:$width,
$args...
);

@include library.button(
$radius:4px
);

@include button using($value){color:$value;}

@include card($radius:4px)using($value,$fallback){color:$value;background:$fallback;}

@include hover{
color:red;
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@include button;

@include clearfix();

@include size($width, $height: $width, $args...);

@include library.button($radius: 4px);

@include button using ($value) {
	color: $value;
}

@include card($radius: 4px) using ($value, $fallback) {
	color: $value;
	background: $fallback;
}

@include hover {
	color: red;
}

```
